          <p>Property Care started with a simple belief: that honest work and attention to detail still matter. What began as weekend landscaping projects for neighbors in Longmont has grown into a full-service property maintenance company trusted across four counties.</p>
          <p>We're not a franchise — we're your neighbors. Every project, from a simple mow to a complete hardscape build, gets the same care we'd put into our own yards. No cutting corners, no surprise charges, just reliable work done right.</p>
